-- Switchblade --

"We're heading back to the Predacon base with these supplies." 
Switchblade doesn't bother further elaborating, as he brings the 
ship slowly around the last obstacle before the Predacon base comes 
into full view.

The large and long Maximal Freighter, now the Pred base, was 
slightly sunk in the partially marshy ground around it. Switchblade 
pulls the cautiously around the base, and lands it's storage bay 
beside that of the freighter.

"We're here." He says, observing the Pred base.

"Megatron," he says as he opens a commlink to the Pred he thoughtwas 
still the commander, "Switchblade here, I've arrived with that cargo 
ship that Flicker gave us. Phoenix, a new bot Tyrant, and I will 
start unloading it into our storage bay."

Switchblade leaves the control room, and heads to the storage bay.


> Phoenix::
> 
> Being naturally curious, Phoenix changes to robot form and follows 
> him inside - not that she actually understands much of this 
technical 
> gobbledygook.



> Tyrant: So where are we going anyway?
